*   [Long Eaton](/Long_Eaton_(MCR)_railway_station) (The original [Midland Counties Railway](/Midland_Counties_Railway) station, not to be confused with the current one)
*   Stapleford and Sandiacre
*   Stanton Gate
*   Trowell
*   [Ilkeston Junction and Cossall](/Ilkeston_Junction_and_Cossall_railway_station) – remarkably, this one was eventually reopened as [Ilkeston](/Ilkeston_railway_station)
*   Shipley Gate
*   Codnor Park and Ironville
*   Pye Bridge
*   Westhouses and Blackwell
*   Doe Hill.

