**The following, on the original [North Midland Railway](/North_Midland_Railway) line:**
Even the foundational [North Midland Railway](/North_Midland_Railway) route saw its stations rationalised:

*   [Wath North](/Wath_North_railway_station)
*   [Darfield](/Darfield_railway_station)
*   [Cudworth](/Cudworth_railway_station)
*   [Royston and Notton](/Royston_and_Notton_railway_station)
